snippet.title: Free Credit Report Commercial
snippet.description:
The best song ever about free credit reports. Just look at the comments on this video for proof.

*Thank you for all the comments and views! We didn't know this would be such a hit! As of May 29 we have 91,000 views!*

--------------------------------------

Well I was shopping for a new car, which one's me

A cool convertible or an SUV

Too bad I didn't know my credit was whacked
'cause now I'm driving off the lot in a  used subcompact

F-R-E-E that spells free
credit report.com baby

Saw their ads on my tv
thought about goin' but was too lazy

Now instead of lookin' flyin' roling phat, my legs are stickin' to the vinyl and my posse's getting laughed at

F-R-E-E that spells free,
credit report.com baby!

*Now don't lie; you can't say that's not an awesome song.
